<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="revise-v">revise <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /rɪ'vaɪz/    美 /rɪ'vaɪz/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>修订；修正：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>revise rules 
修正规则</p></div>

<h4 id="2-review-study">2.★ <strong>复习；温习 (review / study)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I spent the weekend revising for my exam. 
我花了整个周末来复习备考。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>The old rules have to be <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (修正) because they only applied to the circumstances that existed when they were made a hundred years ago.  （2014 湖北改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. revised  </p></div>